# FIoT-Client Python

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

The FIoT-Client Python is a Python library that eases the use of IoT and Context APIs from FIWARE platform.
